{"tid":1141333,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"高達G之復興電影版第一部將在7月於法國搶先公開","createTime":"2019-05-06T12:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T02:14:16.000Z","uid":251945,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b240e45831dc7b9e2febb83a154657fe89664e","tid":1141333,"uid":251945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:00:13.000Z","msg":"根據富野由悠季監督今天在寶塚大學的演講內容，<br />\n由TV版改編、目前製作中的『ガンダム Gのレコンギスタ』（高達G-RECO）的<br />\n劇場版電影首部曲，將於7月在法國JAPAN EXPO公開，之後再於日本公開上映。<br />\n<br />\n預定五部曲完結的G復國電影版，目前已經製作至第三部。根據訪談說1和2集=TV總集篇而第3集開始是全新劇情。<br />\n<br />\n富野監督演講中亦表示:&quot;老子想宰宮崎駿很久了&quot;。<br />\n&ldquo;進入動畫業界後，會有真正的天才。這些人沒準就坐在你旁邊&rdquo;&ldquo;宮崎駿坐在我旁邊的話我什麼都做不了&rdquo;&ldquo;不過因為想宰的人坐在自己旁邊，所以我才能像傻子一樣追求自己的夢想。覺得自己沒時間呆在那裡。所以我才能自立。我之所以能做出高達這樣的作品。是因為我遇到了宮崎先生，高畑先生。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n好似仲有對巨人的評價，有無高手可以幫忙翻譯一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t6yXtuC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft6yXtuC.jpg&h=98fb5b06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b732fb5502de1b9872a1828cf5bbd62f60eb873","tid":1141333,"uid":71913,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"Who care"},{"pid":"c0cbbfaa8aca78320e1df068169b62c588400288","tid":1141333,"uid":251945,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"動漫台唔發動漫資訊，唔通係攞黎發廢PO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fb2d46100003fdec7042f7a2f7599161886d0c","tid":1141333,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:04:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Who cares</blockquote><br />\n讀完小學未"},{"pid":"1e49d5f64275ebeb15937c43e1a3098fe8a0bf11","tid":1141333,"uid":52477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"G復就好似東漢末年獻帝咁 UC皇室血統 但恨鐵不成鋼 又同turn-A炒晒定位"},{"pid":"8cc1b3de4ed8ecf67ee5a03e3fab07db68160c39","tid":1141333,"uid":16515,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:49:07.000Z","msg":"咁垃圾仲出劇場版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76386e1d12cce53d8215e2ce78a20cdca18f24c3","tid":1141333,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"8b88d28e1780a71966269870ec4c2053229fc6fa","tid":1141333,"uid":134665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"好睇 之前有追開"},{"pid":"7169fa39f33008bb2bbc94505fa5f9a83b862fe4","tid":1141333,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:22:02.000Z","msg":"家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c67923a4ebc712b5e1fd26d19ac1bb8bcd6831","tid":1141333,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:14:16.000Z","msg":"都就死，仲睇唔化<br />\n仲係同宮老比落去"}]}